title: Problems
body: Guys i just got yasuo from hextech chest and i rent it the before the rent expired i buy it then when it expired i cant use yasuo but i already bought need help pls i dont know what to do

replies.body:
Hey there,

Definitely sounds like a bug to me, you'll have to [submit a ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/requests/new) for this as Player Support are the only ones who can help you.
